data.description: This home offers a very spacious layout, with four bedrooms, three baths, and an office, on an acre of land.  This provide plenty of space for a garden.  The home needs cosmetic updates, but the bones are solid.  Kitchen range is excluded from transfer.  If a large space is a necessity, don't miss this great home located just outside the Loop.  The pool was operational up until the liner failed.
